<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Birthday Sayang!</title>
    <!-- Link Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&family=Quicksand:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Library Konfeti -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.5.1/dist/confetti.browser.min.js"></script>
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --pink-soft: #ffc0cb;
            --pink-dark: #ff69b4;
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fbc2eb 0%, #a6c1ee 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            border: 2px solid var(--white);
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
            color: var(--pink-dark);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .photo-frame {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid var(--white);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .photo-frame img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: var(--pink-dark);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            background-color: #ff1493;
        }

        #pesan-rahasia {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-style: italic;
            animation: fadeIn 1s;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="photo-frame">
            <!-- Ganti URL di bawah dengan foto cewekmu atau foto kalian berdua -->
            <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1Za9m8xCxZ9BeW9mYRJFgg9DyZnXxv67N" alt="Foto Cantik">

        </div>
        
        <h1>Happy Birthday! 🎂</h1>
        <p>Hari ini adalah hari yang spesial karena seseorang yang luar biasa lahir ke dunia. Semoga harimu penuh tawa dan selalu dikelilingi orang baik disekitarmu! </p>

        <button class="btn" onclick="kasiKejutan()">Klik Untuk Kejutan! ❤️</button>

        <div id="pesan-rahasia">
            "Terima kasih sudah jadi bagian terbaik dalam hidupku. I love you more than words can say!" 🌸
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function kasiKejutan() {
            // Munculkan Konfeti
            var duration = 3 * 1000;
            var end = Date.now() + duration;

            (function frame() {
              confetti({
                particleCount: 3,
                angle: 60,
                spread: 55,
                origin: { x: 0 },
                colors: ['#ff69b4', '#ffffff']
              });
              confetti({
                particleCount: 3,
                angle: 120,
                spread: 55,
                origin: { x: 1 },
                colors: ['#ff69b4', '#ffffff']
              });

              if (Date.now() < end) {
                requestAnimationFrame(frame);
              }
            }());

            // Munculkan Pesan
            document.getElementById('pesan-rahasia').style.display = 'block';
            
            // Ubah teks tombol
            document.querySelector('.btn').innerText = 'Yay! 🎉';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
